# Debug checklist (use when troubleshooting)

1) Confirm request payload:
   - `style`, `size`
   - at least one plugin `enabled: true` with non-empty `sections`
   - `pluginsOrder` matches plugin ids
2) Confirm theme mapping:
   - if `style=default`, `defaultTheme` set
   - if `style=terminal`, `terminalTheme` set
3) Confirm essential configs:
   - production: `userId` present and DB returns configs
   - dev/test: `essentialConfigs` only in explicit test mode
4) Confirm rendering:
   - plugin fetch returns data
   - plugin render returns valid React element
5) Confirm SVG output:
   - contains `id="svg-main"`
   - contains `<foreignObject>`
   - inner HTML root has XHTML namespace
